snippet.title: Take over a  Deinonychus and fight for territory or die trying| Raptor Territory
snippet.description:
Todays live stream is Raptor Territory, this is still a work in progress so expect a lot of patches to be implemented if you have any suggestions feel free to put them down below and ill be sure to forward them to the developer to people improve the game for everyone! The main concept of the game is to take over raptors as they fight over territory over, joining up as a team or working as a solo mayhem the objective is one team or last man standing!
*
store page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1513860/Raptor_Territory/
All the social links make sure you check all platforms for the most content!
Twitter- (normally post game updates/information): https://twitter.com/AcidJurassic
Lurkit-(all in one platform shows all above +yt): https://www.lurkit.com/JurassicAcid
Discord-(open to everyone come hang out): https://discord.com/invite/cA8QnMN
*
